      <p>Hello, this is Cao Minh speaking. If you are reading this message, it means you have seen either <a href="https://x.com/CaoMinh_Touhou/status/1993332139539284403" target="_blank">this tweet</a> or the repository update where this site was hosted. Nevertheless, I am composing this blog with the intention of sharing some of my recent thoughts to everyone reading this.</p>
      <p>I am already on my way to or have arrived at Australia. The reason for that is I am pursuing a Master degree in Computer Science in Sydney, meaning I will be living in Sydney, Australia for at least 2 years. However, moving to a foreign country is not the main reason I started writing blog. The main reason this blog exists is because this is the point where my life is going to turn to a new chapter, and while it seems unnecessary, I think some people would like to know my current status, so I decided to post this announcement before settling down once and for all.</p>
      <p>I will stop going for high-level play and return to a casual Touhou fan.</p>
      <p>I have done very few LNB credits for the past 2 years, and during that period I have been thinking about making this decision. As I grew up and interacted with the world more, I realized the more I attach to LNB and LNN, the more of a burden it becomes for me. I had to make a decision: get LNN for the games I really want before the due date. Thank goodness I managed to achieve the last goal just two months before, and I can finally relax now that I have finished the LNN business.</p>
      <p>For the record, here are my LNNs I have achieved as of this writing:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc">
        <li>Ten Desires - Reimu (2021-03-27)</li>
        <li>Imperishable Night - Border Team Final B (2021-06-12)</li>
        <li>DANMAKAI: Red Forbidden Fruit - Diana (2021-10-16)</li>
        <li>DANMAKAI: Red Forbidden Fruit - Eldied (2022-07-04)</li>
        <li>Imperishable Night - Ghost Team Final B (2022-09-10)</li>
        <li>Imperishable Night - Scarlet Team Final B (2024-05-26)</li>
        <li>Imperishable Night - Magic Team Final B (2024-11-23)</li>
        <li>DANMAKAI: Red Forbidden Fruit - Angelica (2025-09-16)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I probably could have gone for more, but LNN was, and has never been a goal of mine in the first place. I originally only wanted to get better at Touhou STGs in general, but at one point I felt I was so good at Imperishable Night that I thought I could go for LNNFS. Then Touhou World Cup 2021 miracle happened. Then I came to know DANMAKAI and it was my second favorite STG ever after Imperishable Night, which is the reason I went for the LNNs above. To me, LNN is simply a measure of my affection and dedication for my favorite shooting games.</p>
      <p>I have no regrets, even achieving an LNN is more than I could have asked for.</p>
      <p>With all that said, it's time my Touhou journey as an LNN player came to an end, or as the people in my time say, it's time I returned to a secondary fan. I will still follow the latest release of the print works though, but I have achieved great goals, met great people in the community, and made great memories ever since I started playing Touhou 10 years ago. To my online acquaintances, thank you very much, I wouldn't have become who I am today had it not been for your support. My social media accounts will stay active in case anyone wants to contact me, especially since I'm still part of Maribel's LNN list maintaining crew.</p>
      <p>So while I move on with my personal life, I hope the Touhou gameplay community will grow stronger, attract more players and fill Maribel's LNN list and pnd list with more entries regardless of any upcoming conflicts.</p>
      <p>That's all.</p>
      <p>Cao Minh</p>
